quran[25]{c,v,t,f}:
  68,43,"Meso gao gachiteteŵala, ni kuchaunichila kunyosyeka. Nambo posepo ŵaliji nkuŵilanjidwa kuti asujudu (kuswali) ali ŵambonembonepe (ku duniya)."
  68,44,"Basi munekani ni akukanila aji abaliji, chitwajigale mbolembole (wa ku ipotesi) kupitila m’matala gangaakugamanyilila."
  68,45,"Soni ngamba kwalechelesya ŵanganyao, chisimu mpango Wangu uŵele wakulimbangana."
  69,40,"Chisimu jalakwe (Qur'aniji) liŵele liloŵe lya Ntenga Jwakuchimbichika (Jibulilu)."
  69,41,"Ni nganijiŵa jalakwejo liloŵe lya nkwimba chilaanga, yannonope ni yankuikulupilila."
  69,42,"Soni ngaŵa liloŵe lya abimbi, yannonope ni yankukumbuchila."
  70,34,"Ni aŵala ŵanya ŵaakuŵa ali nkwendelechela kusigosa swala syao (pakusiswaliswali)."
  70,35,"Ŵanganyao tachiŵa m’Matimbe ga ku Mbepo ali nkupedwa uchimbichimbi."
  70,36,"Ana chipali chichi kwa aŵala ŵaakufuulu chaakukangamalila kukwenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ ali atunjile meso)?"
  72,28,"Kuti amanyilile (Ntengajo) yanti pamasile paŵaalungwisye (Achimitenga ŵane wosope) mautenga ga M’mbuje gwao, soni nikuti (Allah) ayisyuungwiile yali nayo (paaimanya chenene), soni ni akusenye chiŵalanjilo cha chilichose."
  74,19,"Basi julwesedwe, ana jwapimiile chantiuli!"
  74,20,"Soni julwesedwe, ana jwapimiile chantiuli!"
  74,21,"Kaneka ni jwalolite (ŵandu)."
  75,16,"Ngasin'jitenganyila (Qur’aniji mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) lulimi lwenu (ndema jajikutuluka) kuti n'jikulumisye (kujisunga ni kujisooma)."
  75,17,"Chisimu ili Kukwetu Uwwe kujisonganganya (mu ntima mwenu) ni kumpa ukombosi wakujisooma."
  75,18,"Sano pati tuchinsoomelaga, basi kuyichisyani kusoomwa kwakwe."
  76,10,"“Chisimu uwwe tukogopa kwa M’mbuje gwetu Lisiku lyakuuta sinya (kafili) soni lyakupoteka nnope ni kupwelembwesula (ligongo lya kuleupa kwakwe mu ilagasyo).”"
  76,11,"Basi Allah tachagosa kuyakusakala ya lyele lisikulyo ni kwapa kumelemenda (kungope kwao) ni kusengwa."
  76,12,"Soni tachalipila ligongo lya kupilila kwao Litimbe lya ku Mbepo kwisa soni nguwo sya silika."
  77,7,"Chisimu ichindu yankupedwa chilanga (cha kwisa kwakwe, mpela Kiyama) iŵele yakupatikana (mwangalepeleka)."
  77,8,"Pa ndema ja sichisiimaasidwa ndondwa (kuŵala kwakwe)."
  77,9,"Ni ndema ja lichipesedwa liwunde (nikuŵa mapesa-mapesa)."
  78,4,"Ngwamba! Sampano chaimanye (isyesyene yakwe)."
  78,5,"Soni ngwamba! Sampano chaimanye (isyesyene yakwe)."
  78,6,"Ana nganituliŵika litaka kuŵa chakutandika?"